A vintage 1990s computer magazine illustration showing a fierce orange fox bursting through and shattering a translucent blue "e" shaped window frame, with shards of glass flying outward. The fox is dynamic and powerful, mid-leap, its fur rendered in warm oranges and reds against a muted beige and teal background. Below, an old-fashioned yellow notepad sits on a wooden desk, watching the transformation. The style evokes retro tech magazine covers with slightly exaggerated proportions, halftone dot patterns in the shadows, and a warm nostalgic color palette of mustard yellows, burnt oranges, and faded teals.
